    "code": "---\nid: mobile\ntitle: モバイル\n---\n<div class=\"sm-screen\" style=\"max-width:320px;margin:0 auto;\">\n  <div class=\"sm-header\">お知らせ</div>\n  <div class=\"sm-main sm-col\">\n    <div class=\"sm-card sm-col\">\n      <span class=\"sm-badge\" style=\"align-self:flex-start;\">新着</span>\n      <p class=\"sm-heading\">メンテナンスのお知らせ</p>\n      <span class=\"sm-text\" data-lines=\"2\" style=\"margin-bottom:18px;\"></span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sm-card sm-col\">\n      <p class=\"sm-heading\">アップデート公開</p>\n      <span class=\"sm-text\" data-lines=\"2\" style=\"margin-bottom:18px;\"></span>\n    </div>\n    <a class=\"sm-btn sm-btn-primary\" href=\"#mobile\">もっと見る</a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"sm-footer sm-row\">\n    <a class=\"sm-btn\" href=\"#mobile\">ホーム</a>\n    <a class=\"sm-btn\" href=\"#mobile\">検索</a>\n    <a class=\"sm-btn\" href=\"#mobile\">設定</a>\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
